The Fastway Couriers App has been created to give you greater control and visibility over your courier services and make it even easier to do business with us.

From your internet-enabled iOS device you are able to:

· View full track and trace details of your delivery;

· Order label and flyer bag stock and/or pay for it (if you are 
  a registered customer);

· Request your parcels to be collected (if you are a  
  registered customer);

· Obtain a delivery price quote;

· Log an online enquiry onto our system;

· Submit an enquiry about our available franchises;

· Submit an enquiry to become a customer.

We will be updating the App’s features on a regular basis to bring you even more convenience.
